embeddableConfig.content:
## GCP VPC Flow Logs Overview

Use this dashboard to visualize VPC Flow Logs (OpenTelemetry):
- Shows overall traffic volume over time
- Highlights top source and destination IPs
- Displays top countries traffic volume
- Breaks down protocol usage by flows, bytes, and packets
- Helps identify anomalies and understand network behavior at a glance

query.esql:
FROM logs*
| STATS bytes =  SUM(gcp.vpc.flow.bytes_sent) BY source.address | SORT bytes DESC | LIMIT 10

FROM logs*
| STATS bytes =  SUM(gcp.vpc.flow.bytes_sent) BY source.address | SORT bytes DESC | LIMIT 10

FROM logs*
| STATS bytes =  SUM(gcp.vpc.flow.bytes_sent) BY source.address | SORT bytes DESC | LIMIT 10
